Tool converts the red channel of a PNG into the alpha channel of the same PNG. Color channels in the output file will be filled with a single color; specify which one with the "fillcolor" argument.

Comments in source file may be inaccurate. 

To build:
	make

To build for debugging:
	make DEBUG=1

Usage:
	./badpng infile.png outfile.png fillcolor

